00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:41,760
So maybe saying my grandmother passed away last year, it's a nicer way of saying it.
所以也许说“我奶奶去年去世了”是一种更委婉的说法。

121
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:42,760
Okay.
好的。

